The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Drums and ankle-bells

 ITC Sonar Bangla Sheraton and Towers, in association with Seagram 100 Pipers, Patton and Open Doors, present Dancing Drums, featuring renowned actress-Bharata Natyam danseuse Shobana, in collaboration with Bikram Ghosh on the drums. This exclusively designed programme brings together an innovative, path-breaking musical performance that appeals to the refined tastes of those with an aesthetic bent of mind. Coupled with Shobana?s immaculate style and her inimitable ability to emote, dramatise and communicate through her movements and gestures, Ghosh?s excellent understanding of mood and melody along with his superb sense of rhythm and timing provides all the requisites to make this unique dual performance a runaway success.

 Event: Dancing Drums ? a performance by Shobana and Bikram Ghosh

 When: Today at 7.15 pm

 Where: Pala, ITC Sonar Bangla




